titles.title: A bill to extend until January 1, 1999, the existing suspension of duty on certain unimproved wools.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S3363)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 3/22/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1998, the duty on certain unimproved wools.
